name: Full user story test-case as super admin | UI
description: Create new user, project, build configuration and run it | UI

steps.name: Generate project data
Create project manually with name: sea, id: yu5fxXBFYQ4
Click project selector from header to go to projects page
Click selector: "[data-test-title="Projects"]"
Click selector: "a[title="Create new project"]"
Create project manually
Click selector to create project manually
Click selector: "a[href="#createManually"]"
Fill manual project creation form with name = "sea", id = "yu5fxXBFYQ4", desc=""
Fill selector: "input#name" with text: "sea"
Fill selector: "input#externalId" with text: "yu5fxXBFYQ4"
Fill selector: "input#description" with text: ""
Click create project button with selector input#createProject
Click selector: "input#createProject"
Check if project with id: yu5fxXBFYQ4 was created
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects/id:yu5fxXBFYQ4 with data: None, expected_status: 200
Generate fake build conf data for project with id: yu5fxXBFYQ4
Create build configuration for project with id: yu5fxXBFYQ4
Go to build configuration creation page: http://localhost:8111/admin/createObjectMenu.html?projectId=yu5fxXBFYQ4&showMode=createBuildTypeMenu&cameFromUrl#createManually
Load url: http://localhost:8111/admin/createObjectMenu.html?projectId=yu5fxXBFYQ4&showMode=createBuildTypeMenu&cameFromUrl#createManually
Click selector to create project manually
Click selector: "a[href="#createManually"]"
Fill build conf creation form
Fill selector: "input#buildTypeName" with text: "discover"
Fill selector: "input#buildTypeExternalId" with text: "viFiNoLopdM"
Fill selector: "input#description" with text: ""
Click button: input[name="createBuildType"] to create manual build conf
Click selector: "input[name="createBuildType"]"
Wait for successful build conf creation by waiting selector: div.successMessage:has-text("successfully")
Wait for selector: "div.successMessage:has-text("successfully")"
Check if build configuration with fake build conf id: viFiNoLopdM was created
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects/id:yu5fxXBFYQ4 with data: None, expected_status: 200
Run created build with id: viFiNoLopdM
Go to build conf page with url: http://localhost:8111/buildConfiguration/viFiNoLopdM
Load url: http://localhost:8111/buildConfiguration/viFiNoLopdM
Click run build button with selector: button[data-test="run-build"]
Click selector: "button[data-test="run-build"]"
Go to last launched build and wait for success
Go to launched build url from selector: div.ring-message-description a
Get value of attribute: href from selector: div.ring-message-description a
Load url: http://localhost:8111/buildConfiguration/viFiNoLopdM/302
Wait for selector: div[role="presentation"] > div:has-text("Success") to appear
Wait for selector: "div[role="presentation"] > div:has-text("Success")"
